{"tid":1388884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急救員入","createTime":"2019-07-30T19:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:11:44.000Z","uid":264724,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"02d6e6956ce2515710ecae61046ba79425551686","tid":1388884,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:10:51.000Z","msg":"今日知道 一定會出 胡椒噴霧<br />\n專登買了之 baby shampoo <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">之前 醫生講過 最有效使胡椒噴霧 就係 梘水， 因為胡椒噴霧 帶油性</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但今日 d first aider, 死都用生理鹽水 洗胡椒噴霧， 唔肯用 baby shampoo.<br />\n<br />\n生理鹽水 同普通水一樣 只可洗走表面, 用嚟洗 催淚彈 一定有效<br />\n<br />\n但胡椒噴霧 係另一種 chemical 所以 請 first aider 一定要用 梘水 來洗 胡椒噴霧<br />\n<br />\n之前雨傘運動 個個都係咁用 非常有效"},{"pid":"d288b692cb8d2fe17c8e247ae19bdfaef42a691f","tid":1388884,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:11:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb6ac621c0b87e43012f1e4ede5ede41244a950e","tid":1388884,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:11:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"39d8fe43936d81af894910b4a7608160bd7d9781","tid":1388884,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:11:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e1be82596de08b0812ea7ac7ad179a0737142b95","tid":1388884,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:12:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"994f3a41fdcddae686660ea3e4976a6a2c12e619","tid":1388884,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:16:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b3a94eb785e69d9ef086289bcebeae7afce98cda","tid":1388884,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:16:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b7c2c1779dc6fd158d1f602f6bcc42f5fd1e2ef8","tid":1388884,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm